<DATELINE>LAGOS, Nigeria (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A soldier lost control of a military truck
and it crashed into a crowd of Christmas shoppers, killing 10
people, a newspaper reported Wednesday.
   Thursday's accident happened after the driver made an illegal
U-turn, The Concord newspaper said. It provided no other details.
